items.name: AUTO
desc: specifies the use of a user-defined list.

items.name: AVERAGE
desc: average of all numerical values is calculated.

items.name: COUNT
desc: all values, including non-numerical values, are counted.

items.name: MAX
desc: maximum value of all numerical values is calculated.

items.name: MIN
desc: minimum value of all numerical values is calculated.

items.name: NONE
desc: new values are used without changes.

items.name: PRODUCT
desc: product of all numerical values is calculated.

items.name: STDEV
desc: standard deviation is calculated based on a sample.

items.name: STDEVP
desc: standard deviation is calculated based on the entire population.

items.name: SUM
desc: sum of all numerical values is calculated.

items.name: VAR
desc: variance is calculated based on a sample.

items.name: VARP
desc: variance is calculated based on the entire population.
